---
import EfficiencyChart from './EfficiencyChart.astro';
---
<section class="py-24 bg-slate-900/20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-800 fade-in">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
                    <EfficiencyChart />
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-8 order-1 md:order-2">
                    <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white">Eliminate Context Latency</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        Every time you `git checkout` on a massive repo, you lose seconds to file I/O and minutes to your IDE re-indexing symbols. 
                        With Worktrees, the cost is paid once. Switching is instantaneous.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-blue-500 group hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-colors">
                            <h5 class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-lg mb-1">Parallel Testing</h5>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Run your test suite in the `main` folder while writing code in `feature-login`. 100% uptime.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-blue-500 group hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-colors">
                            <h5 class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-lg mb-1">Independent Artifacts</h5>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">`node_modules` are isolated. Installing a package on one branch never breaks another.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-blue-400 group hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-colors">
                            <h5 class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-lg mb-1">Configuration Sync</h5>
                            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Automatically synchronize environment variables, IDE settings, and build configurations across all active worktrees.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
